  plantName: Maple Tree
  description: "A maple tree is a deciduous tree or shrub belonging to the genus
    Acer (family Sapindaceae), known for its distinctive palmately lobed leaves,
    vibrant autumn colors, and winged \"helicopter\" seeds. Widely distributed in
    the Northern Hemisphere, they are used for timber, syrup, and shade, with over
    100 species ranging from 10\u201345m tall."
